tool_description:
Real-time data, unofficial API zillow.com, search for-sale and rental listings.
Zillow is a leading real estate website in the United States that provides information on buying, selling, renting, and investing in properties such as homes, apartments, and condos.
name: Zillow com
title: Zillow com

api_list.name: properties/search

required_parameters.name: location
required_parameters.description:
Required: true
`location` can be retrieved from /properties/auto-complete endpoint(data->display)
Ex: `Houston, TX`

optional_parameters.name: views
optional_parameters.description:
Surrounding views (status=forSale)
Views (status=forRent)
It can input multiple values, and the values should be separated by commas
Ex: `city,mountain`
`city`: City
`mountain`: Mountain
`park`: Park
`water`: Water

optional_parameters.name: sort
optional_parameters.description:
Sort by
Default : `for_sale`
Choose one of the values below
`relevance`: Homes for You (with sortType=desc)
`recentlyChanged`: Recently Changed (with sortType=desc)
`daysOn`: Newest (with sortType=asc)
`price`: Price: High to Low (with sortType=desc)
`price`: Price: Low to High (with sortType=asc)
`beds`: Bedrooms (with sortType=desc)
`baths`: Bathrooms (with sortType=desc)
`livingArea`: Square Feet (with sortType=desc)
`lotArea`: Lot Size (with sortType=desc)
`yearBuilt`: Year Built (with sortType=desc)
`rentalPriorityScore`: Default in case status=forRent (with sortType=desc)

optional_parameters.name: touring
optional_parameters.description:
Touring
It can input multiple values, and the values should be separated by commas
Ex: `openHouses,approvedVirtualTour`
`openHouses`:Open house
`approvedVirtualTour`: 3D tour

optional_parameters.name: excludeNullRentalAvailabilityDates
optional_parameters.description:
Hide listings with no date provided (only using in case status=forRent and the
`rentalAvailabilityDate` is inputed)
Ex: `true`
Default : `false`

optional_parameters.name: amenities
optional_parameters.description:
Amenities
It can input multiple values, and the values should be separated by commas
Ex: `haveAirConditioning,havePool`
`haveAirConditioning`: Air conditioning (A/C)
`havePool`: pool
`onWaterfront`: On waterfront

optional_parameters.name: homeType
optional_parameters.description:
Home type
It can input multiple values, and the values should be separated by commas
Ex: `townhome`
`singleFamily`: Houses
`townhome`: Townhomes
`condo,apartment`: Condos/Co-ops/Apartments
`land`: Lots/Land
`multiFamily`: Multi-family
`manufactured`: Manufactured

optional_parameters.name: bedrooms
optional_parameters.description:
Bedrooms
Default : Any
Min and max bedrooms should be separated by commas
Ex: `0,5`
In the case of only having the minimum bedrooms: Ex: `0`
In the case of only having the maximum bedrooms: Ex: `,5`
In case of having both: Ex: `0,5`
`0`: Studio
`1`: 1
......
`5`: 5

optional_parameters.name: haveSingleStory
optional_parameters.description:
Single-story
Default : `false`
Ex: `true`

optional_parameters.name: resultsPerPage
optional_parameters.description:
Total number of record per api call
Ex: `2`
Default: `25`

optional_parameters.name: listing
optional_parameters.description:
Listing
It can input multiple values, and the values should be separated by commas
Ex: `fsba,newConstruction`
`fsba`: Agent listed
`newConstruction`: New construction
`foreclosure`: Foreclosure
`auction`: Auctions
`foreclosed`: Foreclosed
`preforeclosure`: Pre-foreclosures
`fsbo`: Owner posted

optional_parameters.name: hoaFees
optional_parameters.description:
Hoa fees
Default : Any
Choose one of the values below
`0`: No HOA Fee
`100`: 100/month
`200`: 200/month
................
`2000`: 2000/month

optional_parameters.name: rentalAvailabilityDate
optional_parameters.description:
Move-in date (only using in case status=forRent)
Choose a move-in date to view listings available on or before this date
Format: `YYYY-MM-DD`
Ex: `2024-03-16`

optional_parameters.name: rentalAmenities
optional_parameters.description:
Rental amenities(only using in case status=forRent)
It can input multiple values, and the values should be separated by commas
Ex: `largeDogs,smallDogs`
`largeDogs`: Allows large dogs
`smallDogs`: Allows small dogs
`cats`: Allows cats
`parkingAvailable`: On-site parking
`laundryAvailable`: In-unit laundry
`incomeRestricted`: Income restricted
`isFeaturedListing`: Apartment community
`areApplicationsAccepted`: Accepts Zillow Applications

optional_parameters.name: keywords
optional_parameters.description:
Keyword search: Backyard, fireplace, horses, MLS #, etc.
Ex: `fireplace,horses`

optional_parameters.name: space
optional_parameters.description:
Space
It can input multiple values, and the values should be separated by commas
Ex: `room`
`room`: Room

optional_parameters.name: lotSize
optional_parameters.description:
Lot size
Default : Any
Min and max lot size should be separated by commas
Ex: `1000,3000`
In the case of only having the minimum lot size: Ex: `1000`
In the case of only having the maximum lot size: Ex: `,3000`
In case of having both: Ex: `1000,3000`
`1000`: 1000 sqft
`2000`: 2000 sqft
................
`10890`: 1/4 acres
`21780`: 1/2 acres
`43560`: 1 acre
`87120`: 2 acres
................
`4356000`:100 acres

optional_parameters.name: priceRange
optional_parameters.description:
Price range
Min and max prices should be separated by commas
Ex: `160000,1500000`
In the case of only having the minimum price: Ex: `160000`
In the case of only having the maximum price: Ex: `,1500000`
In case of having both: Ex: `160000,1500000`

optional_parameters.name: haveGarage
optional_parameters.description:
Garage
Default : `false`
Ex: `true`

optional_parameters.name: timeOnZillow
optional_parameters.description:
Time on Zillow
It is `sold in last` item in case status=sold
Ex: `1`
`1`: 1 day
`7`: 1 week
`14`: 2 weeks
`30`: 1 month
`90`: 3 months
`182`: 6 months
`365`: 12 months
`730`: 24 months
`1095`: 36 months

optional_parameters.name: seniorLiving
optional_parameters.description:
Senior living
It can input multiple values, and the values should be separated by commas
Ex: `seniorCommunity`
`seniorCommunity`: Hide 55+ communities

optional_parameters.name: includeNoHoaDataHomes
optional_parameters.description:
Include homes with no Hoa data
The includeNoHoaDataHomes only takes effect when `hoaFees` is selected.
Default : `true`

optional_parameters.name: sortType
optional_parameters.description:
Order type
Default : `desc`
Choose one of the values below
`asc`: Ascending (smallest value first)
`desc`: Descending (largest value first)

optional_parameters.name: basementTypes
optional_parameters.description:
Basement types

`finished,unfinished,partial`: Finished and Unfinished
`finished`: Finished
`unfinished`: Unfinished

optional_parameters.name: priceType
optional_parameters.description:
Price type
Default : `listPrice`

`listPrice`: List price
`monthlyPayment`: Monthly payment

optional_parameters.name: yearBuilt
optional_parameters.description:
Year built

In the case of only having the minimum year built: Ex: `2008`

Bathrooms
